<title>FRANCE: Non-residents net sellers French bonds in April.</title>
<headline>Non-residents net sellers French bonds in April.</headline>
<dateline>PARIS 1997-07-10</dateline>
<text>
<p>Figures released by the finance ministry showed non-resident investors sold a net 12.08 billion francs of French government bonds (OATs and BTANs) in April, making the total net sales so far in 1997 12.01 billion.</p>
<p>The ministry gave the following unadjusted breakdown (in billions of francs) of the financial account in its balance of payment figures.</p>
<p>						 April   March  April 96</p>
<p> DIRECT INVESTMENT			 -4.97    -4.76   -1.03</p>
<p>     - French investment abroad     -10.15   -13.83  -11.94</p>
<p>     - foreign investment in France   5.18     9.07   10.91</p>
<p> PORTFOLIO INVESTMENT		    14.58   -51.00   10.78</p>
<p>  Residents in foreign securities    11.62   -39.98   12.25</p>
<p>     - shares			     -17.41    10.58    1.74</p>
<p>     - bonds				 27.49   -41.93  -10.85</p>
<p>     - money market instruments	-0.82   -10.83   20.57</p>
<p>     - derivative products		2.35     2.20    0.79</p>
<p>  Non-residents in French securities  2.96   -11.02   -1.47</p>
<p>     - shares				 5.10    -0.74    7.27</p>
<p>     - bonds				  2.37    -3.92  -11.85</p>
<p>     - govt securities(OATs, BTANs) -12.08   -10.76   -8.09</p>
<p>     - money market instruments	-4.51    -6.36    3.11</p>
<p> OTHER INVESTMENTS			-41.99    36.46  -36.21</p>
<p>  Credits				   -17.15    14.88   18.55</p>
<p>  Liabilities			     -24.84    21.58  -54.75</p>
<p> RESERVE ASSETS			    -7.32    -4.69   -0.17</p>
<p> TOTAL FINANCIAL ACCOUNT		-39.70   -23.99  -26.63</p>
